## Commands

| Command | Purpose |
|---------|---------|
| `/search` | Search the codebase semantically |
| `/enrich` | Annotate a symbol with intent and relations |
| `/ingest` | Rebuild the search corpus from source files |
| `/status` | Show enrichment coverage and system health |
